Name: Average time from SW-EIC Accept to Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Accept' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants that include First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum time it takes Awaiting Assignment to Batch to occur after First Look-Your updates are due in one week

Name: Average cycle time of Awaiting Assignment to Batch across all process variants ending with Manuscript Export Succeeded

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting EIC Decision to Awaiting Assignment to Batch in accepted manuscript trajectories

Name: Average time until Awaiting Assignment to Batch is performed following First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Time elapsed between First Look-Please submit updates and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in high-performance variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'First Look-Please submit updates' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Minimum time for Awaiting Assignment to Batch to be executed after Manuscript Export Succeeded in the final phase of the review process

Name: Time from SW-EIC Accept to Awaiting Assignment to Batch relative to the time from SW-EIC Accept to Manuscript Export Succeeded

Name: Cycle time of Awaiting Assignment to Batch in comparison with the cycle time of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation

Name: Average time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurred at least once
